                                                                                          <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>1. Where is Gulabi Kantha Trek located?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>

<meta charset="utf-8" /><b style="font-weight:normal" id="docs-internal-guid-dbb1d08d-7fff-7471-09da-10222e829119"></b></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt"><b style="font-weight:normal" id="docs-internal-guid-dbb1d08d-7fff-7471-09da-10222e829119"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">The Gulabi Kantha Trek is located in the </span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">Tehri Garhwal district of Uttarakhand</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">, near the small village of </span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">Nainbagh</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">. It lies close to the famous Yamunotri valley.</span></b></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>2. What is the height of Gulabi Kantha Trek?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>

<meta charset="utf-8" /><b style="font-weight:normal" id="docs-internal-guid-0dd67112-7fff-b7e9-188c-a975e585668e"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">The trek reaches an altitude of around </span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">12,000 feet (3,658 meters)</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap"> above sea level.</span></b>
<br /></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>3. What is the total distance of the trek?</span>
